name: Battle Rope

name: Treadmill

description: Adding weight training to your workout routine along with cardio exercise and a healthy diet is a great way to support weight loss. .

name: Burpees
description: Burpee is an intense bodyweight move. It isn't an exercise that you can master in a day. It requires extreme training, a strong core and powerful muscle strength. But once you have perfected the move, you can burn tons of calories even in a quick 15-minute session.

name: Workout
description: Regular physical activity can improve your muscle strength and boost your endurance. Exercise delivers oxygen and nutrients to your tissues and helps your cardiovascular system work more efficiently.
